{"article_id":"TjUWxtV7VyzgzaI2","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"\" The wall or the steel barrier .","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"They can have any name","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"they want .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"But we have to have it. \"","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"President Trump often repeats the same things","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"when talking","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"about why he wants a southern border wall .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"\" The crime. \"","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"\" Drugs. \"","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"\" American jobs. \"","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"While there is little evidence","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"these problems are caused by unauthorized immigration","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"or that any of this will be helped by a wall ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"he has remained steadfast .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"\" I will build a great , great wall. \"","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"\" You need that wall. \"","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"\" We can do without a wall. \"","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"But","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"as the fight over border security has dragged on ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"here ' s how he ' s expanded his argument .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"He ' s always said","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"it was about securing the border .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"But recently , Trump has emphasized","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"that he believes","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"building the wall is the moral and compassionate thing","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"to do .","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"\" This is the cycle of human suffering","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"that I am determined to end . \"","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"And he says","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"a wall will benefit people on both sides of the border ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"addressing what he is calling -","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"\" This is a humanitarian crisis , a crisis of the heart and a crisis of the soul. \"","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"But Democrats say","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"the current situation at the border was escalated by Trump ' s policies .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"\" A challenge","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"that President Trump ' s own cruel and counterproductive policies have only deepened. \"","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"So who does Trump think","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"will benefit ?","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Over time , Trump has named many groups","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"he says","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"will benefit from a wall .","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"It started as the - \" American worker. \"","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"And then expanded to -","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"\" Legal residents. \"","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"And - \" And our vets. \"","depth":14},{"id":46,"text":"\" Our immigrant communities. \"","depth":15},{"id":47,"text":"\" Asian-Americans. \"","depth":16},{"id":48,"text":"\" Hispanic-American communities. \"","depth":17},{"id":49,"text":"\" African-American workers. \"","depth":17},{"id":50,"text":"\" It ' s also what our professionals at the border want and need. \"","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"How will Trump pay for the wall ?","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"After some discrepancies","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"regarding the wall ' s price tag -","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"\" $ 6 billion. \"","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"\" Probably $ 8 billion. \"","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"\" Maybe $ 10 or $ 12 billion. \"","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"\" $ 18 billion. \"","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"\" $ 5.7 billion for a physical barrier. \"","depth":14},{"id":59,"text":"Trump has modified his claim","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"that Mexico is going to pay for the wall .","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"\" Mexico - \" \" will pay - \" \" for the wall .","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"100 percent. \"","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"It ' s gone from -","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"\" They don ' t know it yet ,","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"but they ' re paying for it. \"","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"To -","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"\" It may be through reimbursement ,","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"but one way or the other Mexico will pay for the wall. \"","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"And - \" The border wall would very quickly pay for itself. \"","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"And finally , what will Trump ' s wall look like ?","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"Trump ' s vision for the wall itself has also changed over time .","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"Early on , Trump said","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"the wall would be -","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"\" It ' s going to be a Trump wall .","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"It ' s going to be a real wall. \"","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"\" An impenetrable , physical , tall , powerful , beautiful - \"","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"\" A serious wall. \"","depth":15},{"id":78,"text":"\" This is a wall","depth":16},{"id":79,"text":"that ' s a heck of a lot higher than the ceiling. \"","depth":16},{"id":80,"text":"\" It ' s going to be made of hardened concrete","depth":15},{"id":81,"text":"and it ' s going to be made out of rebar and steel. \"","depth":15},{"id":82,"text":"Now , it ' s sounding more like this :","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"\" I never said","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"I ' m going to build a concrete -","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"I said","depth":15},{"id":86,"text":"I ' m going to build a wall .","depth":15},{"id":87,"text":"Just so you know ,","depth":15},{"id":88,"text":"because I know","depth":16},{"id":89,"text":"you ' re not into the construction business. \"","depth":16},{"id":90,"text":"\" Steel is stronger than concrete. \"","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"\" It ' s a new design , highest technology. \"","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"\" Walls","depth":16},{"id":93,"text":"that you can see through. \"","depth":16},{"id":94,"text":"\" It will be a steel barrier rather than a concrete wall. \"","depth":15},{"id":95,"text":"So , will his latest push end with a wall ?","depth":2},{"id":96,"text":"There ' s still a tough political fight ahead .","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":193,"left":192,"right":96,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":192,"left":191,"right":95,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":106,"right":190,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":106,"left":100,"right":105,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":0,"right":99,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":98,"right":3,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":98,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":102,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":4,"right":101,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":104,"left":7,"right":103,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":103,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":190,"left":112,"right":189,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":112,"left":109,"right":111,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":109,"left":108,"right":13,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":108,"left":107,"right":12,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":107,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":14,"right":110,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":110,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":189,"left":130,"right":188,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":130,"left":126,"right":129,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":116,"right":125,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":116,"left":114,"right":115,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":114,"left":17,"right":